Subject: [PATCH] rtc: optee: fix memory leak on driver removal
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: a531350d2fe58f7fc4516e555f22391dee94efd9
